What is CSS?
- get used to searching modules on mdn website
    - eg, for color module: mdm color
- Check browser compatibility table, eg: mdm font-family browser compatibility

CSS:
- Rule based language, changing style (PROPERTY | SELECTOR)
- Works with markup language
- Cascading: Rules that govern how selectors are prioritised

Getting Started:
- Add css to html, same folder, + <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
- rel = we have stylesheet; href = location
